name: tsw_meterread
ssql: select t1.id,t3.name AreaName,t1.kh ClientNo,t1.hm ClientName,t2.watermeter_no MeterSeal,t2.address MeterAddress,t5.watert_name FeeKind,now() CreateDate from ys_cust_userbase t1 join ys_cust_watermeter t2 on t1.id = t2.cust_userbase_id join ys_cb_area t3 on t1.area_no = t3.area_no join ys_cust_yspz t4 on t1.id = t4.cust_userbase_id join ys_price_watertype t5 on t4.fyhlx = t5.watert_no
